At this time I stopped watching NBA but I was still aware of what was going on with the Raptors, They were a winning team due to agreed outcomes. 2018 rolled in, and the NBA did what they do best and sacrificed players so that Toronto can be given a championship so that it didn't seem obvious to the "fans".
